name: Unidentified Farming Object
description:
Keep the Alien alive!

Play as a farmer trying to keep an angry alien fed to save humanity!

Farm and Manage Crops!

Farm and manage crops to produce food for the alien! Make sure to keep them watered to avoid them dying! Gain points from farming to upgrade your items!

Controls

  • WASD - Walk
  • Left Mouse - Interact
  • 1-4 - Change Items
  • Escape - Pause
